A proclamation against selling of ships to foreigners. Caption title. Actual printers' names and suggested publication date from STC. In heading: "selling of shippes". Formerly STC 7901. Identified as STC 7901 on UMI microfilm reel 455. Reproduction of the original in the Bodleian Library.
